footer.credits: Orbital Temple jẹ iṣẹ-ọnà nipasẹ Edson Pavoni, ti a ṣẹda ni ifowosowopo pẹlu Pedro Kaled, João Pedro Polito, Victor Baptista & João Victor Alves, André Biagioni, VK, Jonathan Querubina, Guilherme Bullejos, Eduardo Dias, Roberta Savian Rosa, Clara Marques, Sathi Roy, ati gbogbo awọn ti o tẹsiwaju lati firanṣẹ si tẹmpili yii.
